				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/10/10/17803-pourquoi-les-pigeons-ont-raison-de-protester?replytocom=87888#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-87888", "87888", "respond", "17803")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
		</article>
